result.title: Humana Extends TailorCare Tie-Up to Enhance MA Member Health
result.text: HUM expands its TailorCare partnership to Dallas and Denver, aiming to boost MA member health and cut MSK-related costs.

result.title: TailorCare Expands Value-Based Musculoskeletal Care for Humana Medicare Advantage Members in Dallas and Denver
result.text: NASHVILLE, Tenn.--(BUSINESS WIRE)--TailorCare, a leading provider of value-based specialty care solutions for musculoskeletal (MSK) health, today announced plans to expand its partnership with Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) into Dallas and Denver. Humana Medicare Advantage (MA) members who qualify for these programs will now have access to TailorCare's personalized, evidence-based MSK navigation and care coordination support.
